  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A right rectangular prism has a length of <math alttext=\"11\"><mn>11</mn>\n</math> meters, a width of <math alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn>\n</math> meters, and a height of <math alttext=\"10\"><mn>10</mn>\n</math> meters. What is the volume, in cubic meters, of the prism?</p>",
